<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Visiting information</h3>
<p>We encourage relatives and friends to visit patients. Specific visiting times can be checked on the BHR Hospitals website - www.bhrhospitals.nhs.uk. If the times are difficult for you, please tell the nurse in charge of the ward as it may be possible to arrange alternative times.<br/><br/>If you have an infectious condition such as a cold or stomach upset, please contact the ward for advice before visiting.<br/><br/>There are usually restrictions on the number of visitors per patient and the admittance of children on to the ward. Once again, please check the BHR Hospitals website - www.bhrhospitals.nhs.uk.</p>
